summary: 该插件用于检测WebSphere Application Server是否存在CVE-2020-4643 XXE漏洞，通过发送特定的HTTP请求并验证响应来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the WebSphere Application Server has the CVE-2020-4643 XXE vulnerability, confirming the existence of the vulnerability by sending specific HTTP requests and verifying the response.
